{"word":"ἐξόπιθεν","slug":"ἐξόπιθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξόπιθεν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic for <a href='S:ἐξόπισθεν'><el>ἐξόπισθεν</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>behind, in rear</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Preposition'><a href='S:Preposition'>prep.</a></a> with <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>behind</i>, <el>ἐξ. κεράων</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}